Python is preinstalled on Linux server 
to confirm enter the command "pythin --version"

here is the installation steps for ubuntu
sudo su
apt-get install python3
apt-get install python3.9 -y

Configuration >>>
cd cpython
./configure --prefix=$HOME/python3.9
./configure --enable-optimizations --prefix=$HOME/python3.9
##test the above config using below command
echo $HOME
